1996;;Talk to Me;;American;;Graeme Campbell;;Yasmine Bleeth, Veronica Hamel;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk_to_Me_(1996_film);;Diane Shepherd is an idealistic talk-show producer, who is conscience-stricken, when she clashes with her ratings-obsessed and ruthless talk-show executive boss. Diane is forced to produce a tantalizing program about a prostitute which potentially harms the prostitute, who is trying to turn her life around.<br><br>Kelly Reilly is a teenaged mother whose life is exposed on The Howard Grant Show. Kelly desperately wants to lead a normal life, but society is dragging her back down.